Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.96,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,This is actually pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.34,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.96,Note,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Kappa, literally meaning "river-child", is a water sprite found in Japanese folklore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.35,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.47,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:49.27,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Why a kappa all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.11,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, what does she mean by "is cool, isn't it?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.32,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:03:00.88,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I might want to draw something in fantasy that's interesting and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.78,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Something like a Daidarabotchi and a kappa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.78,Note,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Daidarabotchi is a gigantic demon in Japanese mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.85,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa... Heh, I guess he will be the "uke".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.85,Note,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: In yaoi, "uke" refers to the more feminine partner.{the two participants are referred to as 'uke' and 'seme', where the 'uke' partner is the feminine one who 'catches' and the 'seme' partner is the masculine one who 'pitches'.} {oh god we are NOT doing a 4-line TL Note}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.67,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa, kappa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.00,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.79,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kappapaa... pa... pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.35,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.93,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,With this, maybe we can just play shiritori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.93,Note,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: Shiritori is a Japanese word game in which the players are required to say a word which begins with the final kana of the previous word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.93,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.14,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.39,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Parashite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.39,Note,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: In Japanese, parasite is read as "Perasaito", but Yukko read it as "Parashite".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.52,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,This is what a parashite's meant to be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:33.60,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Having this arrow means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.57,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She's inviting me to a game of shiritori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.19,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.99,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Parashite...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.16,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,"Te"... "Te"... OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.71,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.79,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, a "tengu"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.87,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,She read parasite's "to" as "te".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.18,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. A "tengu," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.57,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,"Tengu"... "gu"... "gu"... "gu"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.78,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,"Gu{\fscx300}-{\r}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:03.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.34,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Tengo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.06,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is a "tengo"?! What's a "tengo"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.93,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.73,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a high school student would make such a childish mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:18.32,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she already drew a picture of tengu and still wrote down what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.97,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.39,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:27.74,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go with "go" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.79,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.29,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this Goku drawn out of boredom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.29,Note,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Goku is a character from a classical Chinese novel "Journey To The West".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:43.61,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... Wait... Goku? I'm pretty sure I drew a tengu just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:49.04,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can understand how she could mistake "gu" for "go".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.85,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get juice from her later for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:55.39,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's "u"... "u"... "u"... OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.70,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,A sea urchin? No, a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.70,Note,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Sea urchin is "uni", and rabbit is "usagi", or "usa" for short, in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.66,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.66,Note,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: Cow is "ushi" in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.52,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,This cow is beyond terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:16.25,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.05,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Tongue! She came at me with the tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.05,Note,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: In Japanese, tongue is "shita".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.68,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's "ta".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.51,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,, "Ta"... "ta"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.84,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi... Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.64,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:37.35,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,If you write it like this, it isn't a taxi. It's a taxy!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:44.40,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to write down whatever works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.45,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, seafood has started to come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.08,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,She's really up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.70,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.36,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.00,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lose like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.00,Note,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: There is no word in Japanese beginning with the sound "n", so you lose if you use a word ending with the kana "n" in a game of shiritori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.67,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, this... I just have to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.58,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to do, Sekiguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,OK, Sekiguchi, let's have a "Isse no se" match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.89,Note,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: "Isse no se" is a Japanese numbers game played using both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isse no two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sekiguchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to do, anyway. Can't you play with me sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.93,Default,Sekiguchi,0000,0000,0000,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sekiguchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:14.87,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my homework and was made to stand in the hallway, Mogami river. By Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:23.38,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I have to stand in the hallway just because I forgot my homework today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:32.01,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,How should I spend this time, Mogami river. By Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.10,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Wai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:49.15,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone! It's a deer... It's a deer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.57,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why is the principal is trying to catch the deer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.91,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wai{\fscx300}-{\r} Principal... D-Deer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.45,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:16.43,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, everyone... The principal's... dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.19,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a... shika senbei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.19,Note,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Shika senbei are rice crackers specially made to feed deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:35.61,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wai{\fscx300}-{\r} Everyone, the principal is dy-dyin{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:37.66,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,He got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:46.17,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,He climbed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:50.00,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.55,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,And falls down just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.77,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,He climbed up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.14,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,He climbed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.65,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's in a deadlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.17,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.57,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Principal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:20.03,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-{\r} Everyone... Death... Principal... Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.33,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Wai{\fscx300}-{\r} Um... Uh...{started too late}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.37,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-{\r} Everyone, listen!{ended too late}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:10.96,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um... P-Prin...{started too late}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.30,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Prin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.60,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing new to report from the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:32.02,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,She said those words from the bottom of her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:39.72,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They were by no means to cover up for the principal, nor because explaining it would be too troublesome. Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:47.91,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she just wanted to show respect to the heroes who had just performed a fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:57.84,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to gather the early-summer rain, Mogami river.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.93,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.51,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,OK, then. Mio-chan will be the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.85,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a judge for ten yen soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.28,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand, do you? It's all about the feeling, the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.74,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kickoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.03,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.71,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me from any angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.79,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:10.47,Default,Hakase+Nano,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock, next comes paper. Go splat like a pear, rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.09,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,I{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.54,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.62,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.78,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:45.24,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a cockroach...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.72,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,C-Carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll have to do it carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:58.26,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make sure this disgusting root of evil doesn't spread in the house again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:01.51,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,A plan... I have to go with the most perfect plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, pesticide spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:10.36,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a one-hit-kill, so there's a chance that it will just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.52,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Most of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.31,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see it squirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.31,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right! What about detergent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:23.65,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover the tea table with detergent to seal its movement, and then pinpoint it directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.24,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I-It will fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,With nowhere to run, it'll definitely fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.68,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,When it flies, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.29,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It'll blindly aim somewhere and hit people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,If this was to hit my body... or hit my face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:52.31,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I-If this was to get inside... get inside my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.10,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one-shot rock and roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.85,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst kind of uneasiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.61,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:06.49,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,The choice of lifting this bowl up might kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.74,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Death or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.12,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.67,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,There's no choice but to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.25,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.71,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:26.55,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:31.41,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inside this, there is a r-roach... a roach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.68,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.89,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a cockroach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.60,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped. All right. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.56,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,That'll save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.29,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.44,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:53.91,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? I'll get it, so lift the bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.54,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:15:01.66,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm saying lift the bowl. Otherwise, I can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:04.97,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:13.97,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?! How could I lift the seal on the root of evil?! This is Pandora's box! The moment I lift it up, it's death or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.29,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.02,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to get it without lifting up the bowl!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.68,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Lift it up yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.31,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,As if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.08,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.36,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san has gone somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.70,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.62,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,What's today's snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.62,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.79,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,The professor is not bothered by bugs either, so surely she can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:49.88,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, i-it'd be nice if you could get rid of t-this cockroach inside this bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.38,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.68,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rock and roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.59,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, then I shall leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:16:02.31,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK. I'll do it in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.37,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.37,Note,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: "Men" is what you say after successfully hitting your opponent's head in kendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:07.73,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hit the wrong one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:17.99,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm... I'm seriously worried here, but this person is... this person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:22.21,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I hate you, professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:27.88,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:36.72,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a joke! Geez, there's no way I would hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.22,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.32,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.32,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.74,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Nano!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:02.49,Default,Narator,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time to rock and roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.70,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's hot, so can I get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.45,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We just got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.30,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,But it's gotten hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.60,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get out after a count to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.21,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,20 log root 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.02,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.27,Default,Hakase,0000,0000,0000,,You said we can get out once we count to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.77,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:33.48,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,You have to say "One, two"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:44.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's with everyone? Just because they have cram school, they all leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sekiguchi, you're bored as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:57.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come to think of it, didn't you go to cram school, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.44,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.66,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko, how's the curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.35,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.90,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.63,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.33,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan, how are things over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.09,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,I foresee a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.84,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.22,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It seems like it's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.66,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:53.40,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,The extremely delicious super-curry is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.01,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I think it will take a little longer over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:04.04,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,We should have started these before the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.54,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say, "Even if a baby is crying from hunger, don't remove the lid".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.40,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we should have brought mayonnaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.59,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You really need mayonnaise for curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.55,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayo-Ma{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.67,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko, what do you like with curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:27.89,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:34.55,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's not like that... T-This is... not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.40,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I still have{\fscx300}-{\r} Look, I still have tokoroten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.40,Note,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Tokoroten are strips of gelidium jelly (agar).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.68,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tokoroten... Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.87,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.20,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Mio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.62,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.71,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What is the colour of your blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.98,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.43,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,There's not any curry or rice for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.20,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.94,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,There's still tokoroten, if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.37,Default,Mio+Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.50,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,Release.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:49.26,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then There's one tokoroten here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.81,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Only one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:54.65,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should take turns eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:58.98,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,However, as we are to blame, Mai-chan, you should start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:06.28,Default,Mio+Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:10.42,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure you don't eat all of it in one bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:14.00,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,That's upsetting to me... I'm not a demon, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.67,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dig in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.34,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I choked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:57.97,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Let's play cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:58.63,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:01.75,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,If things continue this way, this'll end as a disappointing camping trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:05.51,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards at the very last moment and give it a happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:13.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:15.38,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:17.87,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:20.26,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Adults drink alcohol at times like these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:21.58,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:23.88,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mai-chan, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:30.29,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I brought some!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:33.35,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,T-That can't be, Mio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.61,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.60,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,A delinquent. There's a delinquent here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:37.66,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:45.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,A-Any bottle is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.51,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan stop it! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.68,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,We still have Mai-chan's left!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.85,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,This is cider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:24.63,Default,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Exit the bath, drink milk, act drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:27.13,Default,Peso,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a peso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:28.84,Default,10-yen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ten yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.76,Default,Wadoukaichin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wadoukaichin!
